thread.title: Magnus
thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Magnus

author: Magnus
title: Magnus
text: The staff at the local facility is great! I am not so happy with the call center. I filled out a reservation form online clearly stating when I wanted to rent the unit. The next day I got a call from the call center and rent started that day, not the day I had requested which was a week out. So I had to pay rent for that extra week that I didn't want. I told the representative that I didn't want the unit yet but he said I had already rented it and that he couldn't change it. I thought this was a really cheap trick to get more rent out of people!!
